"from\": 379, \"to\": 392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's all about originality and it's all about bringing something new to the table and representing your country or region,\\\" Gilian explained during a press conference, perCNN, noting Gunn's moves.\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 579, \"end\": 583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999999953261067, \"rank\": 4.672574003861481e-09, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"originality\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 422}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 460}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 477}, {\"ngram\": \"your country\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 507}, {\"ngram\": \"region\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 517}, {\"ngram\": \"Gilian\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 526}, {\"ngram\": \"a press conference\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"perCNN\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is exactly what Raygun was doing, she got inspired by her surroundings, which in this case, for example, was a kangaroo.\\\"\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 615, \"end\": 621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.680754383919646e-54, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her surroundings\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 669}, {\"ngram\": \"this case\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 689}, {\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"a kangaroo\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And while Gunn's moves went viral on social media, Gilian emphasized that the judges table was fairly unphased.\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 732, \"end\": 736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999999953261067, \"rank\": 4.672574003861481e-09, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 771}, {\"ngram\": \"Gilian\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 779}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges table\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 812}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She created some original moves which could be maybe funny or entertaining for others, but for us, she basically represented breaking and hip hop,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 993, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some original moves\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 921}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 933}, {\"ngram\": \"hip hop\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She was trying to be original and bring something new to the table.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1062, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From our perspective, that was nothing really shocking.\\\"\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1119, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our perspective\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, other members of the breaking community expressed concern over the less-than-positive responses to Gunn's performance.\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1229, \"end\": 1233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999999953261067, \"rank\": 4.672574003861481e-09, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other members\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1143}, {\"ngram\": \"the breaking community\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"concern\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1187}, {\"ngram\": \"the less-than-positive responses\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That should not happen in our world,\\\" general secretary of the World DanceSport FederationSergey Nifontovsaid, per CNN.\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1366, \"end\": 1369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2921985799697867e-35, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our world\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1286}, {\"ngram\": \"the World DanceSport FederationSergey Nifontovsaid\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1360}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Something is going in the wrong direction.\\\"\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Something\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrong direction\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For her part, Gunn-who failed to earn any points during her Aug. 9 performance- understands that not everyone will see the artistry of her moves.\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1562, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her part\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"any points\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1465}, {\"ngram\": \"her Aug. 9 performance-\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1496}, {\"ngram\": \"not everyone\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1526}, {\"ngram\": \"the artistry\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1548}, {\"ngram\": \"her moves\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, she stands by her participation in the Paris games.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1609, \"end\": 1614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.23372080076564e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her participation\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1601}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was never going to beat these girls on what they do best-their power moves,\\\" she shared ata press conference Aug. 10.\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1743, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these girls\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1661}, {\"ngram\": \"their power moves\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1700}, {\"ngram\": \"ata press conference\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What I bring is creativity.\\\"\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1773, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"creativity\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1771}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indeed, it was most important to Gunn that her routine at theParis Olympicsbe original.\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1808, \"end\": 1812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999999953261067, \"rank\": 4.672574003861481e-09, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympicsbe original\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Creativity is really important to me,\\\" the 36-year-old added.\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1926, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Creativity\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 1875}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I go out there, and I show my artistry.\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my artistry\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes it speaks to the judges, and sometimes it does not.\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 2029, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2001}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do my thing, and it represents art.\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my thing\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2043}, {\"ngram\": \"art\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is what it is about.\\\"\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2094, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Keep reading for more controversies from the 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2155, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more controversies\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2131}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jordan Chiles Medal Controversy After the U.S. gymnast won bronze in the women's gymnastics individual floor exercise final, the Romanian Gymnastics Federation and Romanian finalistsAna Maria BarbosuandSabrina Maneca-Voinea, who came in fourth and fifth place, filed an appeal with the Court of Arbitration for Sport.\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2157, \"end\": 2170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}, {\"begin\": 2287, \"end\": 2317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Romanian Gymnastics Federation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_Gymnastics_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 2322, \"end\": 2330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/