 \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2605}, {\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2636}, {\"ngram\": \"a one-minute deadline\", \"from\": 2709, \"to\": 2730}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The court agreed and ruled that the U.S. athlete's initial score of 13.666 would be reinstated, a decision also adopted later by the International Gymnastics Federation, which said in a statement that it had modified the rankings to put Barbosu in third place.\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2993, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2866, \"end\": 2901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Gymnastics Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The court\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2742}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. athlete's initial score\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2797}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2928}, {\"ngram\": \"the rankings\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 2962}, {\"ngram\": \"Barbosu\", \"from\": 2970, \"to\": 2977}, {\"ngram\": \"third place\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 2992}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympics Committee then announced that it \\\"will reallocate the bronze medal to Ana Barbosu (Romania),\\\" adding, \\\"We are in touch with the NOC of Romania to discuss the reallocation ceremony and with USOPC regarding the return of the bronze medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 2995, \"to\": 3259, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2999, \"end\": 3031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympics Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committ